NEM is a "smart asset" blockchain which supports the cryptocurrency XEM..
1__ `_ ` `_____ `_____ `_________ `____ `_______ `__ `_____________ `____ 
Digital currencies are dominating the world of investing following the surge in the price of Bitcoin in late 2017..
`______ `_________ `__ `_________ `__ `____ `_ `________ `________ `__ `____ `_ `__ `____ `_ 1______ `_ `___ `_____ 
NEM, or New Economy Movement, has the currency symbol XEM and was launched on March 31, 2015..
`___ `_ `__ `______ `________ `__ `__ `_______ `_____ `__ `__ `__ `_______ `_ `____ `__ `_____ 
And while most other cryptocurrencies are developed or "forked" from other codes, NEM was written from scratch using Java script..
`__ `____ `___ `____ `_______________ `__ `________ `_ `_______ `___ `____ `_____ 1__ `__ `______ `___ `______ `____ `___ `_______ 
Around 1,500 early investors bought XEM stakes with one stake being the equivalent of 2.25million XEM coins..
`_____ `____ `____ `________ `_____ `__ `_____ `___ `__ `____ `____ `__ `_________ `_ `__________ `__ `______ 
A blockchain is a digital ledger where all transactions created using cryptocurrencies are recorded..
` `_________ `_ ` `______ `_____ `____ `__ `___________ `______ `____ `_______________ `__ `_________ 
A "smart asset" blockchain allows users to customize their own blockchain creating their own specific "smart contract"..
` `_____ `_____ `_________ `_____ `____ `_ `________ `____ `__ `_________ `_______ `____ `__ `_______ `_____ `__________ 
This means users can create places on the NEM blockchain where they can safely put their digital assets..
`___ `____ `____ `__ `_____ `_____ `_ `__ 1__ `_________ `____ `___ `__ `_____ `__ `____ `______ `_______ 
